{"id":7764,"date":"2025-12-29T13:28:56","date_gmt":"2025-12-29T06:28:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=7764"},"modified":"2025-12-29T17:19:22","modified_gmt":"2025-12-29T10:19:22","slug":"arbutin-la-gi-cong-dung","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/arbutin-la-gi-cong-dung\/","title":{"rendered":"Arbutin \u2013 Ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng da an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Arbutin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201cphi\u00ean b\u1ea3n d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9\u201d c\u1ee7a hydroquinone, mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng, m\u1edd n\u00e1m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1edd t\u00ednh an to\u00e0n cao v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c, Arbutin l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n quen thu\u1ed9c trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng da, tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m sau vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-arbutin\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Arbutin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><b>\u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Arbutin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t glycosyl h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a hydroquinone, c\u00f3 trong l\u00e1 c\u00e2y bearberry (uva ursi), vi\u1ec7t qu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 l\u00ea. Khi v\u00e0o da, enzyme \u03b2-glucosidase s\u1ebd t\u00e1ch Arbutin th\u00e0nh hydroquinone t\u1ef1 do \u1edf m\u1ee9c vi m\u00f4, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf melanin nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7767\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7767\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7767 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-4.webp\" alt=\"Arbutin th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-4-768x528.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-1-4-600x413.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Arbutin th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i:<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> C\u00f3 hai d\u1ea1ng ch\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u03b1-Arbutin &#8211; Alpha Arbutin: t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p sinh h\u1ecdc, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u03b2-Arbutin &#8211; Beta Arbutin: chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed: Arbutin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 19 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase, gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh melanin.<\/span><\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-arbutin\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Arbutin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang, \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u: nh\u1edd \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf tyrosinase v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a melanocyte.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1edd th\u00e2m sau vi\u00eam (PIH): k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi TXA ho\u1eb7c Niacinamide \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng n\u1ec1n da t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean: kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ea9y tr\u1eafng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u00f9ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe, gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng: c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng: nhi\u1ec1u nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u cho th\u1ea5y \u03b1-Arbutin 1\u20132% c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t sau 6\u20138 tu\u1ea7n, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng hydroquinone nh\u01b0ng dung n\u1ea1p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7765\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7765\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7765 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/85-3.webp\" alt=\"So s\u00e1nh \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Hydroquinone v\u00e0 Alpha Arbutin\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/85-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/85-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/85-3-768x528.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/85-3-600x413.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7765\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">So s\u00e1nh \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Hydroquinone v\u00e0 Alpha Arbutin<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-co-che-hoat-dong-cua-arbutin\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m &amp; C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Arbutin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>\u1ee8c ch\u1ebf enzyme tyrosinase:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ng\u0103n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i tyrosine th\u00e0nh DOPA \u2013 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p melanin.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p melanin:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 \u1edf t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u00e1y bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da theo c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf sinh h\u1ecdc t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u1ee8c ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng oxy h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a hydroquinone:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u1ea3m stress oxy h\u00f3a t\u1ea1i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n hydroquinone:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb oxy h\u00f3a nhanh, \u00edt g\u00e2y vi\u00eam ho\u1eb7c bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, Arbutin gi\u00fap l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m v\u00e0 m\u1edd th\u00e2m m\u00e0 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-thuong-gap\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Serum\/Essence:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 1\u20132% \u03b1-Arbutin ho\u1eb7c 3\u20135% \u03b2-Arbutin.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> 1\u20137%, d\u00f9ng to\u00e0n m\u1eb7t ho\u1eb7c v\u00f9ng n\u00e1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 (mask, ampoule):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Vitamin C, Niacinamide,&#8230; t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb (spot treatment):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p TXA, Kojic acid ho\u1eb7c Cysteamine.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_7768\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7768\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7768 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-3.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arbutin (tham kh\u1ea3o)\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-3-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7768\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng theo n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 Arbutin (tham kh\u1ea3o)<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-uc-che-nam-gsc\/\">Kem n\u00e1m Alpha Arbutin 7% GSC<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-thuc-phoi-hop-thuong-gap-voi-arbutin\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Arbutin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Arbutin + Niacinamide:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Arbutin + Tranexamic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 \u0111a c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3m n\u00e1m b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Arbutin + Vitamin C d\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t (MAP, SAP):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Arbutin + Cysteamine ho\u1eb7c Kojic Acid:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> hi\u1ec7p l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh, n\u00ean d\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Arbutin + Retinol (lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m l\u00e2u n\u0103m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-chong-chi-dinh-khi-dung-arbutin\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd &amp; Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi d\u00f9ng Arbutin<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-7769 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-4.webp\" alt=\"L\u01b0u \u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi d\u00f9ng Arbutin\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/anh-4-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>An to\u00e0n v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft lo\u1ea1i da<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c da sau peel.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Tr\u00e1nh n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao (&gt;7%) n\u1ebfu da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y bong nh\u1eb9.<\/p>\n<p>Lu\u00f4n d\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ban ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai &amp; cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c arbutin kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 an to\u00e0n, do h\u1ea5p thu qua da r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\/articles\/PMC8301119\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200chttps:\/\/pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\/articles\/PMC8301119\/<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Arbutin. (n.d.). Go.drugbank.com. https:\/\/go.drugbank.com\/drugs\/DB11217<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Boo, Y. C. (2021). Arbutin as a Skin Depigmenting Agent with Antimelanogenic and Antioxidant Properties. <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Antioxidants<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">10<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">(7), 1129. <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.3390\/antiox10071129\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.3390\/antiox10071129<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Arbutin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201cphi\u00ean b\u1ea3n d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9\u201d c\u1ee7a hydroquinone, mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng, m\u1edd n\u00e1m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1edd t\u00ednh an to\u00e0n cao v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c, Arbutin l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n quen thu\u1ed9c trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00e1ng da, tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m sau vi\u00eam.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7766,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7764","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7764","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7764"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7764\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":7932,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7764\/revisions\/7932"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7766"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7764"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7764"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7764"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}